# app.R
# Church attendance entry app for two Google Sheets
# - One row per date
# - Multiple mobile devices supported
# - Separate submissions for each service and each classroom
# - Prevents duplicate rows by locking + upsert-by-date
# - Saved values for today are shown beside each input
# - Auto-refreshes saved values every 60 seconds
# - Includes a simple in-app login screen for authorized users
# - Uses dedicated app_lock tabs so lock tokens never appear in attendance data tabs
# - Writes rows to explicit rectangular ranges so values cannot drift into wrong columns

